      <title>据称 Paychex 正在洽谈收购规模较小的竞争对手 Paycor</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/paychex-is-said-to-be-in-talks-to-buy-smaller-rival-paycor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Paychex Inc. 正在就收购薪资处理领域规模较小的竞争对手 Paycor HCM Inc. 进行深入谈判。]]></description>
