      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 22:09:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人民币交易员关注中国人民银行汇率调整以判断外汇支撑水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/yuan-traders-look-to-pboc-fixing-to-gauge-level-of-fx-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[人民币已跌破中国去年 12 月一直捍卫的水平，这使得人们再次将焦点集中在人民币的每日参考汇率上，以衡量北京方面支持人民币的意愿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/yuan-traders-look-to-pboc-fixing-to-gauge-level-of-fx-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 22:02:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
