      <title>前黑石交易员 Chu 出价 18 亿美元收购 Insignia</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/cc-capital-makes-takeover-bid-for-australia-s-insignia-financial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚财富管理公司 Insignia Financial Ltd. 已收到 CC Capital Partners 提出的 29 亿澳元（18 亿美元）的收购要约，CC Capital Partners 是由前黑石集团交易员 Chinh Chu 创立的快速崛起的家族理财室。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/cc-capital-makes-takeover-bid-for-australia-s-insignia-financial</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 21:50:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
